                    "value": "Each person places one hand through the strap on the back of their paddle and stand opposite of each other. Then one person throws the ball to the other, and he or she tries to catch the ball with their sticky paddle. Games like these will help your child improve their hand-eye coordination while promoting physical activity. All of the game components are made of durable materials, so the game can be played inside or outside making this a great option for picnics, beach parties, pool parties, and outdoor events. The sticky paddle design will help reduce the risk of injuries, and there's less chance that the ball will be lost during playtime.",
